snippet.title: Has Johnny Depp Been Vindicated?
snippet.description:
#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #TheSun

Johnny Depp has had his day in court and now many wait with bated breath?    The question remains, has he been vindicated, or is he everything Heard and The Sun said he was?   Join Phalon as she talks about this article!
